      "title": "Parliament sessions limited to 3-days due to fuel crisis",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Essential Public Services Act will be approved by Parliament without debate on Wednesday, the Parliament media unit said today.",
        "The House is expected to take up an adjournment debate on the present situation of the country which will be moved by the opposition on the same day.",
        "Meanwhile, Parliament sessions will be confined to three days this week due to the ongoing fuel crisis.(YP)"
      ],
